Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.02,0:01:48.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Lawrence!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.98,0:01:51.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Lawrence!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.62,0:01:55.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wipe yourself off.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.91,0:01:57.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.65,0:02:02.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to leave my scent on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.19,0:02:05.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.23,0:02:15.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She asked me to take part in a large business scheme.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.79,0:02:18.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That fox?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.47,0:02:19.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,To be precise, Abe.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.40,0:02:24.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That female merchant and the landlord here, Harold.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.78,0:02:28.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't confirmed it's trustworthy yet, and of course haven't yet agreed to take part.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.56,0:02:29.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.35,0:02:30.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.65,0:02:31.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The profits are..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.46,0:02:33.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Worth more than my temperament?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.77,0:02:38.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.51,0:02:46.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems the Fifty-man meeting decided on allowing sale of furs to foreign merchants, with one condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.47,0:02:48.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your source?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.50,0:02:50.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The church.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.13,0:02:52.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though they turned on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.18,0:02:56.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We may have parted on unfriendly terms, but I still have contacts on the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.48,0:02:58.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And what are the conditions?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.76,0:03:03.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,They are not to accept anything but cash as payment for fur from foreign traders.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.70,0:03:07.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no one who would take large amounts of cash with them when traveling from afar.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.48,0:03:15.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means, if you can ready a large amount of cash, buy up the quality furs,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.01,0:03:19.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,then sail down the Roam river and sell it off earlier than anyone else...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.42,0:03:20.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.81,0:03:22.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even accounting for the customs tax,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.03,0:03:24.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,you'd get back three times your cost.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.14,0:03:28.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd profit twice your investment?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.90,0:03:31.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.63,0:03:35.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't even know Rigolo existed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.85,0:03:39.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm guessing you don't have any contacts here that could lend you money, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.78,0:03:43.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I could prepare a fair amount if I returned to another city.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.65,0:03:46.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have the time to procure funds so leisurely.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.37,0:03:50.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The fur in this city will be bought up in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.73,0:03:53.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But wasn't the purpose of the meeting to avoid furs being bought up?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.95,0:03:55.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,On the face of it, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.84,0:04:00.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But the fur trade in this city is about to go bust.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.66,0:04:04.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There are a lot of wealthy people around who want to buy up the stock.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.45,0:04:07.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That'll be their capital for getting out?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.43,0:04:13.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I want to get as much money as I can to procure the maximum possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.42,0:04:16.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a fight between merchants.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.94,0:04:18.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A trade war.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.11,0:04:20.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A trade war?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.45,0:04:24.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Those on the offensive made their preparations long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.95,0:04:25.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd expect that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.82,0:04:27.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Which is why we must use your companion.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.16,0:04:32.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If we claim your companion is the daughter of nobility, we can sell her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.74,0:04:35.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't think it's possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.10,0:04:43.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Fruhl von Jieterzentel Boland.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.32,0:04:50.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the 11th head of the Boland household, which swears loyalty to the King of Winfiel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.53,0:04:53.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A family with the true title of nobility.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.83,0:04:57.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, we're fallen nobility who have trouble finding the next meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.62,0:04:59.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But the name is grand at least, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.69,0:05:03.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,After falling so deeply into debt that we could hardly buy a crumb of bread,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.58,0:05:06.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I was bought by an upper-class merchant.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.03,0:05:16.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,With my position, I have the means to sell a daughter with the family name.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.28,0:05:18.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.25,0:05:24.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Your companion would easily pass for nobility if we said so.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.64,0:05:27.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,As nobility myself, I can assure you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.36,0:05:30.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course our goal isn't really to sell her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.74,0:05:36.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I know a trading company who will lend us funds for a cut of the profit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.27,0:05:39.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Selling a noble's daughter is just the means.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.56,0:05:46.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We need her as security on the loan in case worse comes to worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.00,0:05:48.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's where I give my assurance as family head.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.65,0:05:56.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not simply asking you to pawn your companion off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.48,0:06:02.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess this is my last opportunity to leave on a pilgrimage.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.62,0:06:06.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I've had several chances in the past,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.46,0:06:08.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,but I couldn't work up the determination.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.81,0:06:13.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me offer you this inn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.13,0:06:18.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that... exactly what your dream is?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.12,0:06:19.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.08,0:06:21.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So why are you hesitating?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.41,0:06:24.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember your dream was to own a store.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.98,0:06:28.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,In which case, I have no right to object.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.53,0:06:30.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But to make you do that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.04,0:06:31.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.06,0:06:35.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.95,0:06:39.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't even like the idea of me trading in this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.57,0:06:47.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I may not show it, but it's tough for me to say this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.89,0:06:51.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.85,0:06:55.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm most content wandering around with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.26,0:07:02.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, the reason I advise you like I know the world's secrets is for my own sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.45,0:07:05.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So honestly, my heart aches.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.27,0:07:10.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You balance profit and danger on a scale and if it looks good, you go for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.37,0:07:15.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd accept the deal without even considering refusing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.66,0:07:18.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And if it appears the person you're dealing with is trying to trick you,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.68,0:07:20.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,you see past it and profit off it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.46,0:07:24.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You used to charge forward, fearing nothing, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.94,0:07:26.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did that nerve go?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.68,0:07:29.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you suddenly turning defensive?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.64,0:07:33.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been pretty selfish up till now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.68,0:07:38.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about time you were a little selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.13,0:07:43.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But no matter how you look at it, pawning you off is....
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.84,0:07:47.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you telling me that's why you were sweating in your sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.63,0:07:48.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you get mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.16,0:07:51.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get mad that you thought I would.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.60,0:07:54.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You really don't get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.57,0:07:58.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.36,0:08:00.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, people like you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.33,0:08:02.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't I your partner?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.44,0:08:06.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Or am I just a little girl you're fond of? {enter pedobear}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.08,0:08:11.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I sacrificed myself for you once.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.39,0:08:14.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But that was in thanks for your kindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.00,0:08:17.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This time around it's not out of gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.26,0:08:18.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Horo...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.75,0:08:22.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So, is there anything else you're worried about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.62,0:08:26.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I'm wary that this is a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.66,0:08:30.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If the person you're dealing with is plotting something, just plan for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.44,0:08:33.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The bigger the plot...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.53,0:08:36.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,...the bigger the profit when you overturn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.15,0:08:39.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised you remember what I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.88,0:08:41.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the sage wolf Horo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.25,0:08:45.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It wouldn't do for my partner to be a boring merchant.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.77,0:08:51.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.39,0:08:52.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.34,0:08:54.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Breakfast, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.86,0:09:05.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks more like a safe than a church.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.06,0:09:15.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,May the Lord bless you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.57,0:09:20.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What, you're not a charity.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.61,0:09:23.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I'm not with the church.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.40,0:09:27.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I'd like to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.34,0:09:34.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ask away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.57,0:09:36.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about the church...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.20,0:09:40.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A long time ago guys like you were everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.43,0:09:42.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to know about their influence right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.36,0:09:45.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad we understand each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.18,0:09:48.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the biggest church in these parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.44,0:09:52.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,From good bread to beans, they'll pass anything around.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.57,0:09:53.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.49,0:09:54.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.49,0:10:02.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The bishop here doesn't just pass food around, he passes money around too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.38,0:10:04.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How would you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.71,0:10:05.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I'd know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.68,0:10:10.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I often see pretty carriages here all lined up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.43,0:10:13.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Lots of pompous-looking people from the city come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.91,0:10:18.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's obvious what their dinner was from the garbage they throw out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.32,0:10:20.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.48,0:10:23.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you used that right, couldn't you return to your original livelihood?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.80,0:10:28.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The Lord says, "Blessed are the poor."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.74,0:10:35.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Could your type truly rejoice over a gift of brown bread and two bronze coins?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.95,0:10:38.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.24,0:10:43.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what you're planning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.45,0:10:49.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But I expect if you try to get on their good side, you'll just end up having your assets stolen from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.19,0:10:55.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,As far as I know, there's only one person who managed to deal with them for a long period of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.50,0:10:59.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And just recently even he was screaming himself hoarse.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.48,0:11:01.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A guy trading stone statues?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.17,0:11:02.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Stone statues?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.45,0:11:05.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, he was dealing in that kind of stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.73,0:11:07.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What, someone you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.18,0:11:09.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, kind of.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.46,0:11:12.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I assumed he dealt in salt.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.31,0:11:13.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Salt?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.86,0:11:15.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why salt?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.79,0:11:20.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes salt spills from the load he takes to the church.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.43,0:11:24.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I know the quality of salt by its smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.32,0:11:27.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't especially good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.44,0:11:33.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The farther from the sea you go, the more valuable salt becomes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.87,0:11:36.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That Abe...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.36,0:11:37.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A salt merchant?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.50,0:11:42.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're visiting quite early again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.97,0:11:46.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How many merchants do you think have quietly come to visit like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.82,0:11:49.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Judging by your beauty, I'd say quite a number.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.82,0:11:54.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder just how many impolite people have thrust {their cocks lololol}bronze coins at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.70,0:11:57.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid I also came to ask something impolite.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.33,0:11:59.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.15,0:12:01.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what do you want to ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.48,0:12:03.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,About the Fifty-man meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.08,0:12:05.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,They seem to have reached a conclusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.41,0:12:08.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard they decided it was okay to sell furs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.59,0:12:11.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Though it seems paying by credit isn't allowed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.59,0:12:13.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,They are not to accept anything but cash.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.28,0:12:16.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like she said, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.09,0:12:18.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.19,0:12:21.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd also like to ask about the church in this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.93,0:12:25.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.74,0:12:32.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't say anything bad,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.65,0:12:34.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,but it's best you don't get involved with the church.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.67,0:12:37.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So there really is a power struggle going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.05,0:12:40.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand the specifics,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.60,0:12:43.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,but it seems they're inviting important people from all around.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.57,0:12:51.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I had to work two full days and nights because they invited some high ranking member of the church.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.60,0:12:54.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,They're steadily hardening their foundations.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.34,0:12:57.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So they're very edgy about their reputation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.64,0:12:59.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,They're being very charitable.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.13,0:13:03.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And if you start wondering where the money came from and talk about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.85,0:13:06.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,there's no knowing what will happen to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.60,0:13:10.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Once the church has their eye on you, you won't be able to stay in the city for long.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.38,0:13:13.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what the populace has decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.62,0:13:17.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it alright to be telling me this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.71,0:13:22.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's special for me just to be talking to you like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.49,0:13:26.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,May I ask why, out of curiosity?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.80,0:13:29.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If I were to put my finger on it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.43,0:13:33.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd say it's because you smell of another woman, I guess.{keiichi-kun~.... mitsuke.....ta!}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.01,0:13:38.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Girls with a bit of confidence start wanting to flirt with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.29,0:13:40.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't anyone ever tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.61,0:13:43.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,For better or for worse, you happen to be the first.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.10,0:13:47.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then that means one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.05,0:13:50.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You only recently met the girl you're with now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.39,0:13:53.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to be a very kind person.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.79,0:13:59.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,While you were wandering around alone, I don't suppose anyone took much notice of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.65,0:14:01.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But when they see you have a girl beside you,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.83,0:14:05.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,other girls start to get interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.39,0:14:10.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If a sheep was just standing there, it would probably be tedious to hunt it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.91,0:14:16.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But if there were a wolf beside it, you'd think "what's so good about that prey?" and want to have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.99,0:14:21.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Which is why I'd like to invite your companion here just once.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.38,0:14:25.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I graciously accept your invitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.27,0:14:27.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That calm face of yours frustrates me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.43,0:14:32.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So you've told me everything like it happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.36,0:14:33.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't hide anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.33,0:14:39.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It appears I need to teach this girl a lesson about territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.36,0:14:43.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But you've really come to know how things work.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.18,0:14:49.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,To train a horse to move without restraints, it's best to have a driver at the reins.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.45,0:14:50.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.22,0:14:53.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.08,0:14:58.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The church is undoubtedly aiming to establish a cathedra in this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.08,0:14:59.61,note,,0000,0000,0000,,TL note: A cathedra is a bishop's throne.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.26,0:14:59.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A cathedra?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.61,0:15:01.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a vital part of the church body.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.78,0:15:06.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If they have one, the bishop goes from one who is given ranks to one who assigns others ranks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.53,0:15:11.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He is granted many privileges and can manipulate power as he likes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.12,0:15:18.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can understand why that fox would want to leave a city where such a person holds power.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.05,0:15:22.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What I don't understand is the reason they ended relations.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.48,0:15:24.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If it were me, I'd put up with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.31,0:15:28.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The church has power that makes it worth the persistence.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.95,0:15:31.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.32,0:15:34.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It almost sounds like you want my opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.92,0:15:36.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.45,0:15:41.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,When there's a huge deal in front of me,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.77,0:15:44.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,anything is fine, I just want to hear someone's voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.81,0:15:48.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you change your mind if I begged you to in tears?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.28,0:15:50.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I refused,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.02,0:15:52.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,you'd be waiting at the inn for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.47,0:15:56.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd make the deal work out and come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.47,0:15:57.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all there is to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.45,0:16:03.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll have grown up when you can say that without blushing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.16,0:16:04.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll work on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.50,0:16:08.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really lively today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.20,0:16:11.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Males really are best when chasing down their prey.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.53,0:16:12.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.67,0:16:15.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,...once in a while you'd like him to turn your way?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.02,0:16:16.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.25,0:16:17.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.67,0:16:21.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If the deal falls through, what happens to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.51,0:16:24.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you'll be pawned off,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.51,0:16:27.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,if we can't repay the money, you'll be sold off somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.09,0:16:31.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that why you were so worried you were groaning in your sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.03,0:16:33.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's part of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.15,0:16:38.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If that happens, I hope my next partner will be a little smarter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.94,0:16:40.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,True.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.18,0:16:44.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiots who can't return money they borrowed deserve to have sand kicked in their faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.64,0:16:50.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well said for a kid who clutched at me begging when I tried to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.71,0:17:04.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm helping you because I believe in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.89,0:17:06.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.24,0:17:18.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, we should head out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.98,0:17:23.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think you're letting your nervousness show too much?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.70,0:17:26.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If I have to put on a show even inside the inn,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.39,0:17:27.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,when am I allowed to let my guard down?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.99,0:17:30.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,When we first met,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.14,0:17:32.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,no, even until recently,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.48,0:17:36.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,no matter where we were, you were always putting on a show in front of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.63,0:17:39.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It was my first time traveling with a woman after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.25,0:17:41.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And I am getting used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.29,0:17:48.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,When we'd just met, you'd get all edgy just from taking me around.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.63,0:17:53.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If I were to hang around with other women now, would your tail also get edgy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.37,0:17:58.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Males slowly peel back their layers like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.57,0:18:03.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,until in the end all you can say is how it wasn't supposed to turn out this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.19,0:18:06.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But when you get close to someone, it turns out like that no matter who it is, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.09,0:18:11.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's like giving bait to a fish you've already caught,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.20,0:18:14.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,but would you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.08,0:18:20.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd say you got onboard on your own, rather than being a 'caught fish', so that doesn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.41,0:18:22.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than giving you bait,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.36,0:18:24.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I should be charging a boarding fee!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.84,0:18:28.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.54,0:18:33.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,In short, don't forget your original feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.69,0:18:37.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. We're going, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.07,0:18:38.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.54,0:18:51.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, it's because we've been journeying together that I can hold your hand like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.95,0:18:52.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.47,0:18:57.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Bards always sing "I want it to be like when we first met" right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.36,0:19:00.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You may be okay with it,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.61,0:19:05.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,but if things stayed like they were when we first met, I'd get too anxious and collapse.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.21,0:19:06.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.43,0:19:10.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be taking care of you when you breathe your last, so don't worry. {she's gonna eat him :X}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.12,0:19:19.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what's your decision after investigating around town? {Abe soooo pimpin'}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.15,0:19:25.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,My instincts as a merchant tell me that what you say is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.91,0:19:26.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.97,0:19:27.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.33,0:19:30.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,there is one thing that concerns me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.45,0:19:31.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And what's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.56,0:19:34.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason you fought with the church and parted ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.50,0:19:40.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I suppose that's reasonable.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.45,0:19:44.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The bishop here is a man who likes power.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.10,0:19:47.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He wants to establish a cathedra in this town,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.71,0:19:51.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,so ultimately, he's aiming to be archbishop.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.01,0:19:52.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Archbishop?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.03,0:19:53.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.07,0:20:00.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was searching for interesting business, I learned of his backroom money dealings.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.01,0:20:04.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,At that time he was dealing in fur using donation money and a trading company he'd brought up since early days.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.50,0:20:07.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But being an amateur, he was always in the red.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.78,0:20:11.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So I gave him a "two birds, one stone" proposition.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.72,0:20:13.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Dealing in stone statues.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.29,0:20:14.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.41,0:20:17.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But it wasn't just selling stone statues.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.01,0:20:20.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Winfiel nobility, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.00,0:20:24.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I know the archbishop who makes all the big political decisions.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.45,0:20:30.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,In return for introducing a good craftsman to you, you offered your connections with the archbishop.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.69,0:20:34.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And you got to sell the processed statues to the city's church.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.43,0:20:39.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The profit wasn't large, but I gambled on the bishop here becoming archbishop.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.68,0:20:43.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But when his foundations firmed up, he started getting rid of possible hindrances.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.77,0:20:47.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even I was cut off, using the recent events as an excuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.71,0:20:51.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Predicting that keeping you by his side, he'd end up dealing with your troublesome demands.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.45,0:20:53.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He was right of course, that was my intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.36,0:20:57.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But rather than waiting for an individual trader to grow,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.74,0:21:01.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,he decided it'd be easier to work with an already large trading company.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.23,0:21:04.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand his reasoning, but I can't accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.41,0:21:07.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.09,0:21:11.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,In which case, it would be hard to turn your stock of statues into money.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.45,0:21:15.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And you can't just wait around for next year's Northern Expedition either.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.59,0:21:24.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.89,0:21:27.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's arrange a meeting to discuss the details then.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.93,0:21:29.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Pleasure doing business.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.71,0:21:40.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That fox's hands were shaking, weren't they.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.58,0:21:43.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She must have been nervous, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.51,0:21:46.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope that's all it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.38,0:21:50.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.42,0:21:51.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.99,0:21:56.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,At the very least you'll fetch 1500 silver coins.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.36,0:23:52.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: Wolf and Parting Determination
